OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' as mosque vandalised
OL,4,Cin suspected hate crime
OL,6,FThe windows of a mosque in Taunton
OL,7,Fhave been smashed in an 'act of
OL,8,Fvandalism', prompting a police CCTV
OL,9,Fappeal.
OL,11,FPolice say the Taunton Central Mosque
OL,12,Fand Islamic Centre on Tower Lane was
OL,13,Ftargeted at around 6.30am on 6
OL,14,FSeptember.
OL,16,FSajjad Jabarkhel, who works at the
OL,17,Fmosque, said the attack has left his
OL,18,Fcommunity feeling "hurt".
