OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' as mosque vandalised
OL,4,Cin suspected hate crime
OL,6,F"There's a sense of hurt and
OL,7,Fdisappointed that this has happened
OL,8,Fand it comes at a cost", he told ITV
OL,9,FNews.
OL,11,F"Most people have lived here for years
OL,12,Fand when something like this happens
OL,13,Fit is painful. In terms of the spirit
OL,14,Fof the community, they see Taunton as
OL,15,Ftheir home."
OL,17,FOfficers are now looking to talk to
OL,18,Ftwo people in connection to the
OL,19,Fincident, which is being treated as a
OL,20,Fhate crime.
