OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' as mosque vandalised
OL,4,Cin suspected hate crime
OL,6,FThe first is described as white,
OL,7,Faround 6ft tall, between the ages of
OL,8,F20-30, with no facial hair, wearing a
OL,9,Fred coat and beige trousers.
OL,11,FThe second person is described as also
OL,12,Fbeing white, short, around 20-30 years
OL,13,Fold, with a ginger beard, wearing a
OL,14,Fred jacket, blue jeans and a white
OL,15,Fshirt.
OL,17,FGideon Amos, MP for Taunton and
OL,18,FWellington, described the vandals who
OL,19,Fcarried out the attack on the mosque
OL,20,Fas "weak and cowardly".
