OL,6,FIn a social media post, he said: "The
OL,7,Fpeople who attacked and smashed the
OL,8,Fdoor of our local community centre and
OL,9,Fmosque just before this morning's
OL,10,Fchildren's event are not welcome in
OL,11,Four town.
OL,13,F"They aren't patriots, they are weak
OL,14,Fand cowardly and I completely condemn
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,F"To those who smash up any part of our
OL,18,Ftown - you will be caught, you will be
OL,19,Fpunished with the full weight of the
OL,20,Flaw and you deserve to be", he added.
