OL,6,F"I visited to show my support to the
OL,7,Ffamilies affected - the police have
OL,8,Fmounted an investigation and are
OL,9,Fcollecting CCTV footage from several
OL,10,Flocal areas."
OL,12,FIn a statement Avon and Somerset
OL,13,FPolice said: "During this incident
OL,14,Fcriminal damage was caused to glass
OL,15,Fwindows at the property and the
OL,16,Fmotivation behind this incident is
OL,17,Fcurrently unknown, but it is being
OL,18,Ftreated as a hate crime.
